## Key Learnings

- Understanding rows and columns in patterns
- Outer loop → controls rows
- Inner loop → controls what to print
- Patterns are based on counting, not formulas
- Increasing pattern → stars/numbers increase per row
- Decreasing pattern → stars/numbers decrease per row
- Numbers pattern → print from 1 to row number
